Oh. Noah.

2152
01:52:06.958 --> 01:52:07.958
[sniffles]

2153
01:52:09.291 --> 01:52:10.625
[Nick] What have you done?

2154
01:52:17.041 --> 01:52:18.166
[whimpers]

2155
01:52:18.958 --> 01:52:19.958
Nick.

2156
01:52:21.708 --> 01:52:23.916
[door opens. closes]

2157
01:52:26.416 --> 01:52:28.416
[tender music continues]

2158
01:52:43.708 --> 01:52:44.708
[pounding on door]

2159
01:52:46.458 --> 01:52:47.625
[door opens]

2160
01:52:50.833 --> 01:52:51.833
[thuds]

2161
01:52:52.833 --> 01:52:54.392
I don't want any trouble.

2162
01:52:54.416 --> 01:52:56.000
[breathes shakily]

2163
01:52:56.916 --> 01:52:58.291
[line ringing]

2164
01:52:59.541 --> 01:53:01.291
-Come on.
-[ringing continues]

2165
01:53:13.833 --> 01:53:15.250
[Michael] Do you wanna sit down?

2166
01:53:18.166 --> 01:53:19.375
No. I think I'm good.

2167
01:53:21.041 --> 01:53:22.250
[inhales deeply]

2168
01:53:27.041 --> 01:53:28.875
What have you got that I haven't?

2169
01:53:31.083 --> 01:53:32.309
Let's not do this.

2170
01:53:32.333 --> 01:53:34.333
-[line ringing]
-Come on. Nick.

2171
01:53:35.375 --> 01:53:37.250
-[ringing continues]
-[sighs] Come on.

2172
01:53:37.875 --> 01:53:38.875
Go on.

2173
01:53:42.375 --> 01:53:43.375
Fine.

2174
01:53:44.791 --> 01:53:45.833
I'm thoughtful.

2175
01:53:47.333 --> 01:53:49.041
I'm emotionally available.

2176
01:53:50.083 --> 01:53:51.625
And I make her laugh.

2177
01:53:54.666 --> 01:53:58.267
And if she were mine.
I would tell every fucker in the universe

2178
01:53:58.291 --> 01:54:02.625
instead of hiding her away
and making her feel unworthy.

2179
01:54:04.000 --> 01:54:05.458
It's all irrelevant. right?

2180
01:54:06.125 --> 01:54:09.333
Because I couldn't steal her.
Nick. even if I tried.

2181
01:54:09.916 --> 01:54:14.642
Because she is obsessed with you.

2182
01:54:14.666 --> 01:54:16.851
[laughs]

2183
01:54:16.875 --> 01:54:18.416
Don't fucking laugh at me.

2184
01:54:19.125 --> 01:54:20.541
<i>Hi. you've reached Nicholas...</i>

2185
01:54:30.166 --> 01:54:31.541
Oh. come on. Come on.

2186
01:54:32.041 --> 01:54:34.041
No one else could've made her leave you.

2187
01:54:36.500 --> 01:54:39.541
You've done this to yourself.
You know that?

2188
01:54:41.583 --> 01:54:43.059
You pushed her away.

2189
01:54:43.083 --> 01:54:45.250
-Don't touch me.
-[chuckles]

2190
01:54:46.541 --> 01:54:47.601
Don't touch me.

2191
01:54:47.625 --> 01:54:48.684
[line beeps]

2192
01:54:48.708 --> 01:54:51.101
Nick. we can't leave it like that. please.

2193
01:54:51.125 --> 01:54:52.976
This is all a huge fucking mess.
and it hurts.

2194
01:54:53.000 --> 01:54:55.017
Just don't do anything stupid.
and call me back.

2195
01:54:55.041 --> 01:54:57.041
-[music continues]
-[Michael chuckles]

2196
01:54:58.541 --> 01:55:00.125
You could've been happy.

2197
01:55:02.541 --> 01:55:05.333
Instead. you broke her heart.

2198
01:55:07.750 --> 01:55:09.666
Fuck. Nick. Please don't do anything.

2199
01:55:10.500 --> 01:55:11.559
Please.

2200
01:55:11.583 --> 01:55:13.583
[music intensifies]

2201
01:55:20.916 --> 01:55:21.916
Oh. shit.

2202
01:55:22.500 --> 01:55:23.541
[gasps] Oh. my God.

2203
01:55:36.083 --> 01:55:37.291
Hey. are you okay?

2204
01:55:38.250 --> 01:55:40.476
Hey. Hey. I'm sorry.

2205
01:55:40.500 --> 01:55:42.101
[tender music continues]

2206
01:55:42.125 --> 01:55:44.833
Look. I'm sorry. I'm so sorry.

2207
01:55:45.625 --> 01:55:47.351
You have to understand.

2208
01:55:47.375 --> 01:55:49.851
I didn't know about you and Sophia. okay?

2209
01:55:49.875 --> 01:55:52.892
It meant nothing. Look at me. Look at me.

2210
01:55:52.916 --> 01:55:55.375
Nick. it didn't mean anything.
I promise you.

2211
01:55:58.500 --> 01:55:59.500
I'm sorry.

2212
01:56:05.250 --> 01:56:06.458
[sirens wailing]

2213
01:56:09.000 --> 01:56:10.809
I have to go now. Noah.

2214
01:56:10.833 --> 01:56:12.767
Nick. what did you do?

2215
01:56:12.791 --> 01:56:14.500
[car doors closing]

2216
01:56:15.333 --> 01:56:16.601
[radio chatter]

2217
01:56:16.625 --> 01:56:17.875
[officer] Nick Leister?

2218
01:56:18.541 --> 01:56:21.809
You are under arrest on suspicion
of assault causing actual bodily harm.

2219
01:56:21.833 --> 01:56:22.892
[handcuffs click]

2220
01:56:22.916 --> 01:56:25.184
You do not have to say anything.
but it may harm your defence…

2221
01:56:25.208 --> 01:56:28.208
[officer continues indistinctly. distorted]

2222
01:56:37.083 --> 01:56:39.083
-[engine starts]
-[no audible dialogue]

2223
01:56:47.208 --> 01:56:49.208
[sirens wailing]

2224
01:56:52.041 --> 01:56:55.041
["Breaking Up Slowly"
by Lana Del Rey ft. Nikki Lane playing]

2225
01:59:12.000 --> 01:59:15.000
["Come Down" by Asha Banks playing]

2225
01:59:16.305 --> 02:00:16.650
